snippet.title: Cannibal Crossing: First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
Cannibal Crossing is a new game I've been helping design. It has a randomly generated open world, base building, drop-in online co-op multiplayer, and pixelated blood explosions!

Please tell your friends if you've been a fan of our previous games, and wishlist it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1304090/Cannibal_Crossing/
